 new heights in preparing thoughtful global citizens for a diverse 21 st century driven by a knowledge economy.  Improving student learning by equipping faculty with novel teaching technologies and techniques.  Creating and refining the state-of-the-art spaces needed by today’s students for learning, living, and discovering.        Read about our outstanding students            Doing Their Part: 2020 Activities Honorary Society Inductees    Posted on April 28, 2020             Chancellor Amiridis Celebrates Donors and Advocates for Supporting UIC    Posted on April 11, 2019             Alumnus who overcame challenges helps others do the same    Taylor Kasper  |  Posted on November 14, 2018        $1.5 million from The Davee Foundation boosts UIC scholarship fund    Brian Flood  |  Posted on July 12, 2018        UIC welcomes the Class of 2018 to the UIC alumni family    Posted on May 23, 2018               UIC launches fundraising campaign to raise $750 million    Sherri McGinnis Gonzalez  |  Posted on October 30, 2017             $3M gift to UIC honors immigrants who lived American dream, helps generations of students    Carlos Sadovi  |  Posted on October 16, 2017             First Impressions    Jonathan Black  |  Posted on April 27, 2017             JACSW 2012 Alumnus Establishes an Endowed Scholarship Fund to "Pay it Forward"    Taylor Kasper  |  Posted on March 13, 2017             Impassioned Medicine: Medical Student Alex Cano    Posted on February 28, 2017                 Make Your Impact  Visit our secure giving form to make a gift supporting students at UIC.   Give Now            IGNITE:  The Campaign for UIC    Back to main content           Give Now    IGNITE Priorities     Support Student Success    Empower Faculty    Drive Discoveries    Connect to Communities    Support A College or Unit      Understanding Giving     Giving Strategies    Gift Planning    How to Give                    UIC Logo        Advancement       Contact   601 S. Morgan Street, 2